@Node Main "ne.guide"



   This file describes `ne', a free text editor which runs on (hopefully
almost) any UN*X machine and on the Amiga. `ne' is easy to use for the
beginner, but powerful and fully configurable for the wizard, and most
sparing in its resource usage.

Copyright (C) 1993 Sebastiano Vigna


